name: Rapaz Esforçado ou Mamãe Está Azul/ Strenuous Boy or Mommy Is Blue
description: Gouache and Water-Based Paint Marker on recycled canvas | 2012 | Inspired in the song Rapaz Esforçado sang by Gal Costa in the concert and album Fa-Tal - Gal a Todo Vapor and also in the testimony of Maria Amélia Teles about when she was shown to her children after being tortured during the military dictatorship in Brazil.
